Package: strainspy
Type: Package
Title: Strain Level Microbiome Wide Association Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Author: Gerry Tonkin-Hill
Maintainer: Gerry Tonkin-Hill <g.tonkinhill@gmail.com>
Description: Strainspy fits statistical models to detect microbial strains 
    associated with a phenotype. For small sample sizes, models can be fitted 
    using empirical Bayes maximum a posteriori (MAP) priors to improve detection 
    power. Supports various experimental design scenarios, including repeated 
    measures.
